title: Silver Surfer (v1 - v6 + Extras) (1968 - Ongoing)
description:
Silver Surfer (v1 - v6 + Extras) (1968 - Ongoing) 


Norrin Radd is the Silver Surfer, an alien from the planet Zenn-La with the power to manipulate cosmic energy granted to him by his former master Galactus. He travels the stars on his trusty surfboard with superhuman speed.


Silver Surfer Annuals (1988 - 1994, 1997 + 1998)

Silver Surfer v1 (001 - 018) (1968 - 1970)

Silver Surfer v2 (One-Shot) (1982)

Silver Surfer v3 (001 - 146) (1987 - 1998)

Silver Surfer v4 (001 - 014) (2003 - 2004)

Silver Surfer v5 (001 - 005) (2011)

Silver Surfer v6 (001 - 003) (2014 - Ongoing)

Plus extras
